        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Family Poverty is Not Child Neglect Act&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill requires states receiving grants for child protective services systems to ensure that such systems are not used to separate a child from the child's parent or guardian for reasons of poverty. &lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
